%h1 New Summary

.row
  .col-md-4
    %p Guidelines for summaries.
    %ul
      %li Make it concise.
      %li Make it fun.
      %li Don't use bad grammar.
  .col-md-8
    = form_for @summary do |f|
      .form-group
        = f.label :description
        = f.text_field :description, class: 'form-control', placeholder: "Enter summary description"

      = f.submit "Save", class: 'btn btn-success'